{"tid":191202,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"渡邊麻友呼籲年輕人做義工","createTime":"2017-04-07T16:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T15:30:13.000Z","uid":3806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37e899d5573b1198de473b6f16e7feca2a67f9ba","tid":191202,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"日本組合AKB48的渡邊麻友昨日率領姊妹組合SKE的木崎Yuria一起參加日本紅十字會的義工招募活動，兩人齊齊穿起圍裙和戴頭巾，參與義務煮食和炮製手握飯團，以及負責分湯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkheadline.com/phototext/images/245(5143).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkheadline.com%2Fphototext%2Fimages%2F245%285143%29.jpg&h=d0bf1531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首次參與同類工作的渡邊表示，實際體驗義工的工作之後，感受到需要年輕人的力量去幫忙，加上為需要幫助的人煮食要靠團體力量才能完成。而木崎就指，希望義務煮食不單填滿受助人的肚，更希望令對方的心靈更加充實。渡邊又透露早前去為小朋友講故事，「最初不知道該如何與他們溝通，但與小朋友接觸後，過程很愉快。」<br />\n<br />\narm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654e01f483783700f2ac4cd42466c3add97de2f4","tid":191202,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T16:24:25.000Z","msg":"唔係成日都做免費雞咩？<br />\n幫啲老人家打飛G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c608073f4ef504d81adf3c880e292bd981b318a2","tid":191202,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T16:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係成日都做免費雞咩？<br />\n幫啲老人家打飛G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫咗你唔好成日將自己嘅嘢拎出來講"},{"pid":"fe83420daa01870b0602c91ff8c5ae8d31d04c86","tid":191202,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T16:33:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係成日都做免費雞咩？<br />\n幫啲老人家打飛G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫咗你唔好成日將自己嘅嘢拎出來講</blockquote><br />\n搞撚錯得一張雞圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時既你唔是咁架啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2a0d9b42c1fd4745c